name: SCE_SHELL_UTIL_ERROR_SYSTEM_CRASH
notes:
Crashing (powerloss) during gameplay or on game startup (works fine in menus)
I used my thermal camera to look at the RAM, GDDR6 - 7 was sitting about 10°C above the other RAM
I swapped that RAM and the console worked (sent back to customer, still working a week later). I used Amaoe Senticil with solder paste.
I beleive this error is cause by RAM that fails under stress, there may be other ways to diagnose. This is my third console I have been able to with this error code. All have been RAM.
